Goldy
An NLP-Based Chatbot for English Learning in Elementary Education

Goldy is a fun, educational chatbot designed for elementary students to boost their English skills. Using advanced NLP with Python's NLTK library through Flask, this interactive tool fosters language learning. Crafted with HTML, CSS (with Tailwind CSS), and JavaScript, and designed using Figma, Goldy makes learning English playful and engaging for young learners.
